ng-lawsuits-attrakt-3525386">“重组”该组合</a>。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fifty-fifty-keena-teases-new-music-from-girl-group-3568275">FIFTY FIFTY 的 Keena 预告了该女子组合的新音乐，该音乐</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 Steam严厉打击游戏中“非法”使用人工智能https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/steam-cracks-down-on-illegal-use-of-ai-in-games-3568326?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=steam-cracks-down-关于在游戏中非法使用人工智能Ryan EasbyWed, 10 Jan 2024 09:54:51 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsVideo Game Culture https://www.nme.com/?p=3568326 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Steam-sales-valve.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="阀门蒸汽" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Steam-sales-valve.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Steam-sales-valve-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Steam-sales-valve-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Steam-sales-valve-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Steam-sales-valve-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Steam-sales-valve-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Steam 更新了 AI 政策</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/steam-cracks-down-on-illegal-use-of-ai-in-games-3568326">Steam 严厉打击游戏中“非法”使用 AI 的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Steam-sales-valve.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="阀门蒸汽" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Steam-sales-valve.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Steam-sales-valve-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Steam-sales-valve-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Steam-sales-valve-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Steam-sales-valve-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Steam-sales-valve-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/steam">Steam</a>宣布将减少提交到该平台的游戏中人工智能内容的使用。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/heartsteel-exo-baekhyun-riot-games-league-of-legends-virtual-artists-3562214">Heartsteel 上的 Riot Games：“Baekhyun 和 Ezreal 的合作是一个梦想”</a></strong></li></ul><p>虽然此前<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/valve">Valve</a>在给<a href="https://www.pcgamer.com/valve-is-scrutinizing-games-with-ai-assets-on-steam-says-avoiding-copyright-violation-is-the-developers-responsibility/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>PC Gamer 的</em></a>一份声明中宣布，在人工智能方面“开发商有责任确保他们拥有发布游戏的适当权利”，但它也承认“正在研究如何将其集成到人工智能中”。我们现有的审查政策”。现在， <a href="https://steamcommunity.com/groups/steamworks/announcements/detail/3862463747997849619" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a>指南的正式发布更新澄清了围绕 AI 的情况。</p><p> Steam 上 AI 审核政策的第一个变化是对内容调查的更新，内容调查是开发者在游戏上市之前向 Valve 提交的。该调查现在将包含一个“人工智能披露部分”，开发人员必须在其中描述游戏如何使用人工智能以及它正在使用两种预定义类型的人工智能中的哪一种。</p><p>这两种类型的人工智能被描述为“预生成”，即在游戏开发过程中使用人工智能创建的任何内容，以及“实时生成”，即在游戏运行时使用人工智能创建的内容。 </p><figure id="attachment_3178082" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3178082" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3178082" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Steam-Deck-top-view.jpg" alt="蒸汽甲板。图片来源：阀门" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Steam-Deck-top-view.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Steam-Deck-top-view-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Steam-Deck-top-view-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Steam-Deck-top-view-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Steam-Deck-top-view-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Steam-Deck-top-view-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3178082" class="wp-caption-text">蒸汽甲板。图片来源：阀门</figcaption></figure><p>在这两个人工智能类别中，开发者必须声明其没有使用“非法或侵权内容”，实时生成的人工智能用户必须描述他们为确保人工智能“不生成非法内容”而采取的措施。</p><p> Valve 还推出了一个系统，允许玩家使用“实时生成”人工智能举报游戏中的任何非法内容。</p><p>声明总结道：“今天的变化是我们提高对该领域的格局和风险的理解，以及与使用人工智能的游戏开发人员和构建人工智能工具的人员交谈的结果。”</p><p> “这将使我们更加愿意在 Steam 上发布使用 AI 技术的游戏。”</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/machinegames">MachineGames 的</a><em><a href="https://www.nme.com/films/indiana-jones">《印第安纳琼斯》</a></em>游戏<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/indiana-jones-game-will-be-revealed-at-xbox-event-next-week-3567791">将于下周首次亮相</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/steam-cracks-down-on-illegal-use-of-ai-in-games-3568326">Steam 严厉打击游戏中“非法”使用 AI 的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
